<https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533/sec/sec1-materials-11-00649/para/0/sent/8> <http://persistence.uni-leipzig.de/nlp2rdf/ontologies/nif-core#anchorOf> "Beside waste heat recovery, TE devices have been investigated for their use in TE-solar hybrid systems [4], TE-refrigeration [7] and as radioisotope TEGs for the deep-space applications of NASAs Voyager and Cassini missions [8]." .
