<https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533/sec/sec2dot1-materials-11-00649/para/0/sent/3> <http://persistence.uni-leipzig.de/nlp2rdf/ontologies/nif-core#anchorOf> "For better readability, the weighted samples are named as TixZryHfzNiSn and the detected phases as TixZryHfzNiSn (roman numerals)." .
