<https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533/sec/sec2dot4-materials-11-00649> <http://www.essepuntato.it/2008/12/pattern#contains> <https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533/fig/materials-11-00649-f008> .
