<https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533/sec/sec3-materials-11-00649/para/0/sent/3> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasGeneratedBy> <https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/activity/parse/PMC5951533/run-2026-06-11> .
<https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533/sec/sec3-materials-11-00649/para/0/sent/3> <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#wasQuotedFrom> <https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533> .
<https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533/sec/sec3-materials-11-00649/para/0/sent/4> <http://persistence.uni-leipzig.de/nlp2rdf/ontologies/nif-core#anchorOf> "After several optimization steps, the stable Heusler phases with the C1b structure Ti0.21Zr0.40Hf0.39NiSn(IV), Ti0.43Zr0.28Hf0.29NiSn(III) and Ti0.68Zr0.17Hf0.15NiSn(I) could be synthesized as a single phase." .
