<https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533/sec/sec3-materials-11-00649/para/1/sent/3> <http://persistence.uni-leipzig.de/nlp2rdf/ontologies/nif-core#anchorOf> "The sample Zr0.5Hf0.5NiSn accidentally meets almost perfectly the stable composition and therefore shows the best thermoelectric properties in this series." .
