<https://kumagallium.github.io/asterism/papers/resource/paper/PMC5951533/sec/sec3-materials-11-00649/para/1/sent/3> <http://persistence.uni-leipzig.de/nlp2rdf/ontologies/nif-core#endIndex> "22861"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger> .
